<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000" size="5">Associate Mentor Application 2016</font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><font color="#cc0000"><br></font></b></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font><span style="font-family: arial;"><b><font>Hey&nbsp;</font></b></span><font face="arial"><b>{!Contact.FirstName},&nbsp;</b></font></font></div><div style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial"><b>Thank you for submitting your Associate Mentor application, and congratulations for getting through to assessment!</b></font></div><div style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial">Please ensure you have completed the following tasks to prepare you for your role (if you haven't already):&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: arial;">&nbsp;</span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b>1) Assessment Events (deadline tomorrow, 5pm)</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="arial">Please ensure that you have registered to come to an assessment event using the password&nbsp;</font><b style="font-size: 12pt;">AM2016</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.&nbsp;</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">These are taking place throughout half term and will give you an overview to the role, training on how to excel in your position, and a chance to meet the staff team.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">We've only got a few spaces left, so hurry!</span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b><a href="https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/associate-mentor-training-tickets-24013069738">Click here to register for an assessment event</a></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);">2) If your going to be 18 or over by the end of August...</b></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: arial;"><font>You will need to have a Disclosure and Barring Service Check (DBS). These could take up to 12 weeks to process so get yours started now! Make sure you choose the option 'Youth Worker' when applying.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; font-family: arial;"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; font-family: arial;"><b><font><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2016DBSinstructionsAMs.pdf">Click here for information&nbsp;and next steps</a></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; font-family: arial;"><b><br></b></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: arial;"><b>If you have any questions then please email tcs.northlondon@the-challenge.org.</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; font-family: arial;"><b><font size="2"><br></font></b></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: arial;">See you at your assessment!&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: arial;">Megan</div>]]></td>
